Screening - Class in application.models
Purpose: Screening class containing fields and methods pertaining to a single screening Description: Contains information about the screening in the form of String fields, a list of seats in the screening (with information on whether or not each seat is booked); along with getter methods and methods for managing the list of seats.
Screening(String, LocalDateTime, HashMap<String, Boolean>) - Constructor for class application.models.Screening
Constructor Sets the Screening's film title, datetime and seats list from the parameters, and constructs a screeningID from them

Constructor Given a JSONObject, sets the fields of the Screening object based on the corresponding key-value pairs in the JSONObject; parses the JSONObject and calls the constructor above.
